{"tid":935783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（香港人質素）覺唔覺而家啲人真係好自私？","createTime":"2018-12-10T09:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T13:47:07.000Z","uid":62597,"like":127,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"ac4a617ceb4734f337cb9a08bc6c5722d92fdf93","tid":935783,"uid":62597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T09:36:13.000Z","msg":"係日常生活層面 好似搭地鐵咁 明明入面就好多位 個個都唔願行入多啲啲 下下都要人再格硬sip下去 <br />\n仲有個啲柱男柱女正一on9 挨撚哂成條柱搞到扶唔到 遇到呢啲情況我都會出聲屌佢 問佢挨撚夠未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有而家final period 諗住係大學圖書館溫書追hon <br />\n明明圖書館大大隻靜字貼出黎 你老味成日都有人大大聲傾計 當正係自己屋企咁 <br />\n住宿舍個班仆街仔仲on9 晚晚嘈撚住哂 完全唔撚顧人感受 <br />\n真係唔好再話咩香港人好撚優越過大陸人 根本大家都係一鳩樣 咁撚閪自私低質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申： 唔係鍵盤戰士 次次遇到呢啲情況都有出聲屌柒條友 只係真係屌到撚攰 上黎發洩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16e6199c8863fcb21e9a4a2d5d920846b5aae85c","tid":935783,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T09:45:07.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該要教育一下"},{"pid":"2afed954326f77ef44bdb1478940ff081d4b485e","tid":935783,"uid":224452,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T09:48:46.000Z","msg":"香港人點會係低質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係無質素<br />\n港蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10371de9644d9982499aa9ccc8e1e09d91e88c05","tid":935783,"uid":48964,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T09:49:25.000Z","msg":"咩而家，幾十年黎都係咁。只不過以前人口冇咁密集，生活壓力細小小，所以比較少衝突"},{"pid":"fdfe0549d4d7db862180b441d8c25f920284a8a0","tid":935783,"uid":170249